III. Challenges:
1. Data Complexity:
Handling mixed sampling rates (seconds vs hourly data).
Managing large datasets with multiple sensor readings.
Difficulty in aligning time-series data.
2. Model Understanding:
Understanding regression models for industrial prediction.
Dealing with highly correlated features (Iron vs Silica).
Deciding whether to include/exclude certain variables.
